1. The position(s) require(s) the ability to type at a minimum speed as designated on the Class Specifications.
2. You must obtain a valid typing certificate confirming your ability to meet the minimum typing speed, prior to being hired.
3. Current version of the State Examination/Employment Application STD Form 678 (when not applying electronically), or the Electronic State Employment Application through your Applicant Account at www.CalCareers.ca.gov.
4. Resume is required and must be included.
5. Authorization to Release Information Form (PO-299): https://www.fire.ca.gov/-/media/D817B8E27D8049C3BC35297686467FB9
